{"tid":2401094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★前Bitcoin交易平台創辦人轉買磚頭　5600萬購跑馬地雲暉大廈低層","createTime":"2021-02-09T12:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T04:16:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"38411c938ee213e1b32b22a8d4bd501246f2f6d7","tid":2401094,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T12:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210208/435568350135848960027146.jpeg/B33mkjNeVgKWRTc6yP9vciH4Uu6M4xn2R1r8UEda_FA?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210208%2F435568350135848960027146.jpeg%2FB33mkjNeVgKWRTc6yP9vciH4Uu6M4xn2R1r8UEda_FA%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=4cc62a44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比特幣（Bitcoin）等虛擬貨幣近年獲熱炒，價格大漲，新近更衝上4.6萬美元關口。不過，曾在港創立首家Bitcoin交易實體店的商人MADDEN HUGH DOUGLAS，新近卻轉為投資磚頭，斥資約5,600萬元購入跑馬地豪宅雲暉大廈低層單位。<br />\n<br />\n據土地註冊處資料，跑馬地雲暉大廈A座低層單位，連一個車位，早前以5,600萬元易手，新買家為MADDEN HUGH DOUGLAS及LY VOCH LIM。前者為上市公司品牌中國（0863）的行政總裁，曾於滙豐銀行、澳大利亞聯邦銀行及美國道富銀行等擔任高管職務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/585239/%E5%89%8Dbitcoin%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%BA%E8%BD%89%E8%B2%B7%E7%A3%9A%E9%A0%AD-5600%E8%90%AC%E8%B3%BC%E8%B7%91%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%9B%B2%E6%9A%89%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%E4%BD%8E%E5%B1%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%2F585239%2F%25E5%2589%258Dbitcoin%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%2589%25B5%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25BD%2589%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E7%25A3%259A%25E9%25A0%25AD-5600%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E8%25B7%2591%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%259B%25B2%25E6%259A%2589%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BB%2588%25E4%25BD%258E%25E5%25B1%25A4&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQl3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=b523fd66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0